40 Wedding Fails That Are Too Funny to Believe!

the call of marriage is one that can not be easily ignored. It’s a deep-rooted  tradition that is supposed to signify the coupling of two souls into one. A magic moment when you become forever together with someone that you love, and whom loves you back equally. But not just the emotional part is important. The actual production itself is equal, or for some, of even greater importance. They want all of the guest, friends, enemies and frenemies to know that they alone had the most magic of days. It is a source of pride for many a bride, and groom. But when you put some much planning into what is supposed to be one of the most special days of your life. The stress and pressure to make sure everything is perfect builds and eventually, something is bound to go wrong. Just check out these hilarious wedding moments. 

I’m Telling Mom!

This bride is probably used to her sister’s shenanigans. It seems as if her sister isn’t the groom’s hugest fan.
